President Biden spoke with President Zelenskyy of Ukraine to congratulate him on Ukraine's Independence Day and to mark 18 months since Russia's invasion of Ukraine. President Biden reaffirmed the US commitment to support Ukraine's defense against Russian aggression and to hold Russia accountable. They also discussed the training of Ukrainian fighter pilots and the expedited approval for other nations to transfer their F-16s to Ukraine to enhance its defensive capabilities. President Biden expressed admiration for the bravery and sacrifice of the Ukrainian people.